description: Forever Yogurt has joined the recent frozen yogurt craze, bringing Chicago endless possibilities of combinations with 85 rotated flavors and over 50 yummy toppings. All of the varieties are gluten-free, non-fat or low fat and contain active, live cultures so in addition to all the known health benefits, there comes undeniably delectable taste, which will surely create a sweet explosion in your mouth.
name: Forever Yogurt
